## 🔄 5. Routing & Navigation

### 5.1. AppWireframe

**File**: `lib/app/app_wireframe.dart`

**SelectProductsScreen Route**:
```dart
SelectProductsScreen.keyName: (context) {
  final args = ModalRoute.of(context)?.settings.arguments;
  if (args != null && args is Map) {
    return SelectProductsScreen(
      initialProducts: args['initialProducts'] ?? args['products'],
      branchId: args['branchId'] ?? args['saleBranchId'],
    );
  } else if (args != null && args is List) {
    return SelectProductsScreen(
      initialProducts: List<Map<String, dynamic>>.from(args),
    );
  }
  return const SelectProductsScreen();
}
```

**Navigation từ CreateOrderScreen**:
```dart
context.navigator.pushNamed(
  SelectProductsScreen.keyName,
  arguments: {
    'saleBranchId': selectedWarehouse?.id,
    'products': selectedProducts,
  },
).then((result) {
  if (result != null && result is List) {
    setState(() {
      selectedProducts = List<Map<String, dynamic>>.from(result);
      _updatePaymentSummary();
    });
  }
});
```

