## 🔧 8. Utilities & Extensions

### 8.1. Price Formatting

**File**: `lib/utils/extension/int.dart`
```dart
extension IntExt on int {
  String toPrice() {
    // Format: 87000 => "87.000đ"
    final format = NumberFormat("#,##0", "vi_VN");
    return "${format.format(this)}${AppConstant.strings.vnd}";
  }
}
```

**File**: `lib/utils/extension/num.dart`
```dart
extension NumExt on num {
  String toPrice() {
    // Format: 87000.5 => "87.000,5đ"
    final format = NumberFormat.currency(
      locale: "vi_VN",
      symbol: "",
      decimalDigits: this % 1 == 0 ? 0 : 2,
    );
    return "${format.format(this)}${AppConstant.strings.vnd}";
  }
}
```

**Usage trong SelectProductsScreen**:
- `variant.price.toInt().toPrice()` (convert double → int → price string)

### 8.2. Address Formatting

**File**: `lib/utils/functions/order_function.dart`
```dart
String renderBaseAddress(BaseAddress? data) {
  final addressArray = [
    data.address,
    data.ward,
    data.district,
    data.province,
  ];
  return addressArray
      .where((item) => item != null && item.toString().trim().isNotEmpty)
      .map((item) => item.toString().trim())
      .join(', ');
}
```

