## 📚 14. Code Patterns

### 14.1. Debounce Pattern
```dart
EasyDebounce.cancel('productSearch');
EasyDebounce.debounce(
  'productSearch',
  const Duration(milliseconds: 500),
  () {
    // Search logic
  },
);
```

### 14.2. Pagination Pattern
```dart
bool _hasMore = true;
int _currentOffset = 0;
final int _limit = 20;

Future<void> _loadProducts({bool loadMore = false}) async {
  if (!loadMore) {
    _currentOffset = 0;
  }
  
  final result = await apiCall(offset: _currentOffset);
  
  if (loadMore) {
    _allProducts.addAll(products);
  } else {
    _allProducts = products;
  }
  
  _currentOffset += products.length;
  _hasMore = _currentOffset < count;
}
```

### 14.3. Variant Selection Pattern
```dart
if (product.hasVariants) {
  _showVariantSelector(product);
} else {
  _addProduct(product, null);
}
```

